content.rendered:
Directed by Nishikant Kamat.

Written by Ritesh Shah.

Cast John Abraham(Kabir Ahlawat). Nishikant Kamat(Kevin Ferriera). Sharad Kelkar(Dilip Sangodkar). Teddy Maurya(Luke Ferriera). Diya Chalwad(Naomi). Kazu Patrick Tang(Atilla). Shruti Haasan(Rukshida Kabir Ahlawat). Prashanti Talpankar(Fisherwoman). Nathalia Kaur(Anna (as Nathalia Pinheiro Kaur)). Paromita Chatterjee(Rich Woman). Akanksha Awasthi(Lady Constable). Viren Vajpayee(Male Constable). Vansh Sanghani(Rich Kid). Jayant Sawarkar(Shop-Owner Uncle). Shivkumar Subramaniam(A.C.P. Rebbelo (as Shiv Kumar Subramaniam)). Uday Tikekar(Maantu). Megh Pant(Football). Shyam Pakakillath(Gun Dealer (as Syam Pokakillath)). Sanjay Khapre(Jay Pitale). Abhijeet Chavan(Francis). Akash Dabas(Kunal Bathena). Nachiket Purnapatre(Edwin). Ghanshyam Sondagar(Cop at Beach). Kunal Naik(Loan Shark). Gurpreet Saini(Viju Dempo). Suhasini Mulay(Carla Aunty). Sachin Pathak(Ernie’s Waiter Sunil). Bobby Bedi(Joaquim). Manju Rawal(Canteen Aunty). Sunil Vishrani(Russian Translator). Sandesh Kulkarni(Debtor). Nora Fatehi(City Club Dancer). Karan Sharma(City Club DJ). Tatiana(City Club Aerial Dancer). Shekar(City Club Smoke Machine Man). Himanshu Joshi(Man on Phone). Ajay Trehan(Mi Officer). Sunil Rodrigues(Assassin Outside Hospital). Dhanvi(Red Frock Girl). Adil(Bagha Kid 1). Bhav Dhulia(Gaming Zone Main Goon). Lakhan Kachole(Gaming Zone Side Goon). Pritesh Shanbhag(Tattoo Parlour Owner). Aditya Bichu(Baga Kid 2). Uday Chandra(Organ Extraction Doctor) . Deependra Singh(Bihari Gagster)

Language Hindi.

Producers John Abraham. Gaurav Bose. Madhav Roy Kapur. Sunir Kheterpal. Sheel Kumar. Ajay Rai. Kuldeep Rathore. Mahipal Karan Rathore.

Production Azure Entertainment. J.A. Entertainment.
